    public interface Readable
extends ReadableASCII, ReadableBinary
    Interface for objects capable of deserialising themselves from ascii and/or binary formats. IMPORTANT: All Readable objects must have a no-arguments constructor, but this CAN BE protected or private.
    Author:
    Jonathon Hare (jsh2@ecs.soton.ac.uk), Sina Samangooei (ss@ecs.soton.ac.uk)
